{"tid":443122,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[是日狗食]自制櫃桶腸粉","createTime":"2017-10-21T10:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T11:45:05.000Z","uid":478,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1829ea02701f479b108803da43628d552b749eb7","tid":443122,"uid":478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T10:38:38.000Z","msg":"是咁的 忽然想食櫃桶腸 但屋企附近個間整得唔好食<br />\n於是決定自己整<br />\n<br />\n架生:<br />\n平底不鏽鋼兜<br />\n鑊<br />\n腸粉刮<br />\n蒸架<br />\n匙更<br />\n筷子...<br />\n<br />\n材料：<br />\n<br />\n炸蒜豉油<br />\n蒜頭 你想就整多d 我就一個<br />\n豉油 隨意<br />\n<br />\n粉漿:<br />\n粘米粉 150g<br />\n澄麵 15g<br />\n生粉30g<br />\n<br />\nOptional:<br />\n雞強 <br />\n肉碎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/21/183739_555798c9d4400b3a284371ea7672744f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F21%2F183739_555798c9d4400b3a284371ea7672744f.jpg&h=fb1f7382&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eaa9ed04abaf53f7228c8da53e9e5b32acb9277d","tid":443122,"uid":478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T10:47:24.000Z","msg":"首先係蒜頭豉油<br />\n原個碎上<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/21/184208_5db48db1f685b56e374b6463a31bdbd0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F21%2F184208_5db48db1f685b56e374b6463a31bdbd0.jpg&h=f213d618&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/21/184224_ad31b2899adfcd5aab982fca6c7e5557.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F21%2F184224_ad31b2899adfcd5aab982fca6c7e5557.jpg&h=5b72e7ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後開火燒熱d油 然後同中火炸佢 當佢d泡開始變大就轉細火 唔係會炸到「窿」哂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/21/184600_fdb1b13fca84d5b0d9245653fdc4ec3d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F21%2F184600_fdb1b13fca84d5b0d9245653fdc4ec3d.jpg&h=c814db7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你想有多d蒜油就蒜同油比例1:2<br />\n我自己就落少左同炸耐左 準備 「窿」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/21/184710_2efe2ffa2910047b9f356c813356970d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F21%2F184710_2efe2ffa2910047b9f356c813356970d.jpg&h=6faa5536&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"438b3af20c9ab36c136245b4814c39e766f199cf","tid":443122,"uid":122264,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T10:54:29.000Z","msg":"重點"},{"pid":"1f8422b5a31bb319a21c87f8df93a4a254284e0f","tid":443122,"uid":29684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T10:58:15.000Z","msg":"頂好正🤤🤤🤤🤤🤤"},{"pid":"46667d1300dabde1322d2f859e844107018f851f","tid":443122,"uid":478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:01:30.000Z","msg":"整完蒜頭 就可以整個漿<br />\n<br />\n張上面個3種粉撈埋再加450g水 開左佢<br />\n(我個制成品就粉左D同埋易散 想煙韌就落多D澄麵 落粉D粘米粉)<br />\n記住MAKE SURE 佢溶哂<br />\n然後再加半湯匙生油(我自己就落多左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"ecb13b3818f27464dc7268e198b14dbf9cb42d76","tid":443122,"uid":478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:01:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整完蒜頭 就可以整個漿<br />\n<br />\n張上面個3種粉撈埋再加450g水 開左佢<br />\n(我個制成品就粉左D同埋易散 想煙韌就落多D澄麵 落少D粘米粉)<br />\n記住MAKE SURE 佢溶哂<br />\n然後再加半湯匙生油(我自己就落多左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote>"},{"pid":"6df93afceab6b3810f9d9900761117b366995230","tid":443122,"uid":478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:02:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/21/190150_9dee65c3ecdaf46e861742e52312c59b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F21%2F190150_9dee65c3ecdaf46e861742e52312c59b.jpg&h=6fc557ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e7a112912f26f324fdff946678733ceb1a6e9d3","tid":443122,"uid":27359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:02:34.000Z","msg":"食食"},{"pid":"c8ac94424047f3b1236f22a7954a7d1610177e46","tid":443122,"uid":478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:09:15.000Z","msg":"拎個鑊煮滾D水佢 放個蒸架係上面 FOR 一陣整腸粉<br />\n<br />\n落D油落個不鏽鋼兜度 然後一勺粉漿 <br />\n要加強就打一隻落去 肉碎都係<br />\n其實想加咩其他材料都可以"},{"pid":"0ab7b6a3cc922a726ab970514ca013c5d1255db6","tid":443122,"uid":478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:11:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/21/191136_9a66db0ac53e3eee0218d9a5ca39c914.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F21%2F191136_9a66db0ac53e3eee0218d9a5ca39c914.jpg&h=ce27a725&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4708d75fbf2e58334715dcf53a526ac8a8e377a","tid":443122,"uid":104213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:13:25.000Z","msg":"正呀喂,未食飯"},{"pid":"6f9393e853a04cc8df70e62cb2f412692a6e1af0","tid":443122,"uid":478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:25:33.000Z","msg":"放上去蒸 3-5MINS<br />\n記住盡量放平 唔係會有窿窿 同埋令到一邊會好厚<br />\n落左豬肉碎既記住肯定佢熟 唔係入廠就關我撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f130ada1fff31fd07ca2a6c2b0c1f745ce82a13c","tid":443122,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:27:03.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4b178d56482b0957043ee736861351193f66e1","tid":443122,"uid":478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:32:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/21/193201_f2ebe4e9b6e341d3938aed36c3eb005c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F21%2F193201_f2ebe4e9b6e341d3938aed36c3eb005c.jpg&h=e0564a00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59cc9ca020fe615cf5fd8a682e1e666a3b794de4","tid":443122,"uid":478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:34:33.000Z","msg":"蒸熟後個樣 無白色既粉漿係度浪下浪下就OK<br />\n盡量張D肉碎整細舊D 唔好堆埋一堆 咁樣豬肉易D熟"},{"pid":"671041f63deda5704195eddefa886c3f86f2a7d2","tid":443122,"uid":101522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:38:27.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c9b28ef640d06e675400eefaa62c16db50677a","tid":443122,"uid":21111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448255509f746f8da6bb1c36cd7ee6a2f76bd7a1","tid":443122,"uid":478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/21/193941_fbe1788f1e94a6f605b49ff5a5becaca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F21%2F193941_fbe1788f1e94a6f605b49ff5a5becaca.jpg&h=7dd91577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n淨粉漿整熟後個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好明題整唔勻循 搞到有窿窿<br />\n<br />\n然後有腸粉刮就刮佢上碟 無就慢慢捲堆上碟<br />\n<br />\n之後炸蒜油加豉油(我用左煲仔飯豉油 因為甜 好食d)<br />\n<br />\n跟住就開餐哂<br />\n<br />\n我上面呢度整左4條都仲有漿淨低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  應該整到5/6條到<br />\n<br />\n下次試下整叉腸蝦腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n完"}]}